q1 -> Find all users who were active in January 2023 and check whether they were also active in February 2023 (retained) or not (churned). Return the user_id, their January activity date, and a column called status with value Retained or Churned. Order by user_id.

Sol 1 -> 
SELECT user_id, activity_date,
CASE 
WHEN feb_flag = 1 THEN 'Retained'
ELSE 'Churned'
END AS status
FROM (
    SELECT *,
           MAX(CASE WHEN MONTH(activity_date)=2 THEN 1 END)
           OVER(PARTITION BY user_id) AS feb_flag
    FROM user_activity
) t
WHERE MONTH(activity_date)=1
ORDER BY user_id;



